text: Saikhom Mirabai Chanu (born 8 August 1994) is an Indian weightlifter. Mirabai Chanu lifted a total of 201 kg, winning the Gold Medal at the CWG 2022. She won the silver medal at the 2020 Summer Olympics in the Women's 49 kg category. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Olympians for India Category:Indian weightlifters
